--- SECTION 3: SUBSTITUTE ---
(Goal: Practice 's' for the current line and line ranges)

A) Single Line Fix:
Move your cursor to the line below. Type ':s/OFF/ON/' to fix only this line.
WiFi: OFF, Bluetooth: OFF

B) Ranged Fix:
Type ':41,43s/OFF/ON/g' to fix part of the block below without touching other lines.
Device1: WiFi: OFF, Bluetooth: OFF
Device2: WiFi: OFF, Bluetooth: OFF
Device3: WiFi: OFF, Bluetooth: OFF
Device4: WiFi: OFF, Bluetooth: OFF
Device5: WiFi: OFF, Bluetooth: OFF

C) Visual Range Fix:
Press 'V' to select the three lines below, then type ':s/TEMP/PERM/g'.
