--- SEARCH & REPLACE CHEAT SHEET ---
/pattern         : Search forward
?pattern         : Search backward
/\%Vpattern      : Search only within Visual Selection
* : Search forward for word under cursor
#                : Search backward for word under cursor
:s/old/new/      : Replace first 'old' with 'new' on CURRENT line
:s/old/new/g     : Replace all 'old' with 'new' on CURRENT line
:'<,'>s/old/new/g: Replace 'old' with 'new' in Visual Selection
:10,20s/old/new  : Replace 'old' with 'new' between lines 10 and 20
:%s/old/new/g    : Replace all 'old' with 'new' in WHOLE file
:%s/old/new/gc   : Replace all with CONFIRMATION for each change
